     C           CUBNYY    IFNE *ZERO
     C                     MOVE CUBNYY    WKY
     C                     MOVE '.'       WKH1
     C                     MOVE CUBNMM    WKM
     C                     MOVE '.'       WKH2
     C                     MOVE CUBNDD    WKD
     C                     MOVE '-'       WKH3
     C                     MOVE CUBNBB    WKB
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    WK02
     C                     END
     C                     MOVE WK02      @MEBAD
     C** DATE OF PECEIVING INSPECTION **
     C           CUKNYY    IFNE *ZERO
     C                     MOVE CUKNYY    KNYY
     C                     MOVE '.'       KNT1
     C                     MOVE CUKNMM    KNMM
     C                     MOVE '.'       KNT2
     C                     MOVE CUKNDD    KNDD
