     C**AFTER  WEIGHING || NUMBER OF BOXES , FRACTIONS * *
     C                     MOVE CURKHK    @HAKO3
     C                     MOVE CURHSU    @TANSU
     C*----- COUNT ----*
     C           CUKAHZ    IFNE WKHZ
     C           *IN34     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVE CTR       @KENSU
